            <fr:title text="The path relation via reflexive-transitive closure">The path <fr:link href="jms-00JH.xml" title="The reflexive-transitive closure of an endo-relation" addr="jms-00JH" type="local">relation</fr:link> via <fr:link href="jms-00JH.xml" title="The reflexive-transitive closure of an endo-relation" addr="jms-00JH" type="local">reflexive-transitive closure</fr:link></fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Corollary</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (A,R\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="jms-00JC.xml" title="Directed graph" addr="jms-00JC" type="local">directed graph</fr:link>. For all <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s,t\in  A]]></fr:tex>, we have <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\mathrel {R^{\circ *}}t]]></fr:tex> if and only if there exists a path with source <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s]]></fr:tex> and target <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[t]]></fr:tex> in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>1</fr:month><fr:day>18</fr:day></fr:date><fr:anchor>7374</fr:anchor><fr:addr type="machine">unstable/6045</fr:addr><fr:route>unstable-6045.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="" /><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>This is an immediate consequence of <fr:link href="jms-00JG.xml" title="Paths and iteration" addr="jms-00JG" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number addr="jms-00JG" /></fr:link>: by <fr:link href="jms-00JH.xml" title="The reflexive-transitive closure of an endo-relation" addr="jms-00JH" type="local">Definition <fr:contextual-number addr="jms-00JH" /></fr:link> we have <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\mathrel {R^{\circ *}}t]]></fr:tex> if and only if there exists <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n\in \mathbb {N}]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\mathrel {R^{\circ  n}}t]]></fr:tex>, which by <fr:link href="jms-00JG.xml" title="Paths and iteration" addr="jms-00JG" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number addr="jms-00JG" /></fr:link> holds if and only if there existss a path from <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s]]></fr:tex> to <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[t]]></fr:tex> in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex> of some length <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n\in \mathbb {N}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
